trans-unit.source: Contains information about an ink gesture.

A <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult> contains an <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> and the level of likeliness that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> correctly identified the gesture.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult>包含<xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>和 likeliness 層級的<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>正確識別手勢。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A> property to determine the level of likeliness that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> correctly identified the gesture.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A>屬性來判斷 likeliness 的層級的<xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>正確識別手勢。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to identify a gesture on an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何在識別手勢<xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>。

trans-unit.source: This example assumes that there is an <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas> called `inkCanvas1` and that its <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas.Gesture> event has been connected to the event handler in the code.
trans-unit.target: 這個範例假設有<xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>呼叫`inkCanvas1`且其<xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas.Gesture>事件已連線至程式碼中的事件處理常式。
